BN-ShMNH ShNH Y'aShYHV BMLKV VShLShYM V'aChTh ShNH MLK BYUrVShLM VShM 'aMV YDYDH BTh-'yDYH MBTShQTh.
VY'ySh HYShUr B'yYNY YHVH VYLK BKL-DUrK DVD 'aBYV VL'a-SUr YMYN VShM'aVL.
VYHY BShMNH 'yShUrH ShNH LMLK Y'aShYHV ShLCh HMLK 'aTh-ShPhN BN-'aTShLYHV BN- MShLM HSPhUr BYTh YHVH L'aMUr.
'yLH 'aL-ChLQYHV HKHN HGDVL VYThM 'aTh-HKSPh HMVB'a BYTh YHVH 'aShUr 'aSPhV ShMUrY HSPh M'aTh H'yM.
VYThNH 'yL-YD 'yShY HML'aKH HMPhQDYM BBYTh YHVH VYThNV 'aThV L'yShY HML'aKH 'aShUr BBYTh YHVH LChZQ BDQ HBYTh.
LChUrShYM VLBNYM VLGDUrYM VLQNVTh 'yTShYM V'aBNY MChTShB LChZQ 'aTh-HBYTh.
'aK L'a-YChShB 'aThM HKSPh HNThN 'yL-YDM KY B'aMVNH HM 'yShYM.
VY'aMUr ChLQYHV HKHN HGDVL 'yL-ShPhN HSPhUr SPhUr HThVUrH MTSh'aThY BBYTh YHVH VYThN ChLQYH 'aTh-HSPhUr 'aL-ShPhN VYQUr'aHV.
VYB'a ShPhN HSPhUr 'aL-HMLK VYShB 'aTh-HMLK DBUr VY'aMUr HThYKV 'yBDYK 'aTh- HKSPh HNMTSh'a BBYTh VYThNHV 'yL-YD 'yShY HML'aKH HMPhQDYM BYTh YHVH.
VYGD ShPhN HSPhUr LMLK L'aMUr SPhUr NThN LY ChLQYH HKHN VYQUr'aHV ShPhN LPhNY HMLK.
VYHY KShM'y HMLK 'aTh-DBUrY SPhUr HThVUrH VYQUr'y 'aTh-BGDYV.
VYTShV HMLK 'aTh-ChLQYH HKHN V'aTh-'aChYQM BN-ShPhN V'aTh-'yKBVUr BN-MYKYH V'aTh ShPhN HSPhUr V'aTh 'yShYH 'yBD-HMLK L'aMUr.
LKV DUrShV 'aTh-YHVH B'yDY VB'yD-H'yM VB'yD KL-YHVDH 'yL-DBUrY HSPhUr HNMTSh'a HZH KY-GDVLH ChMTh YHVH 'aShUr-HY'a NTShThH BNV 'yL 'aShUr L'a-ShM'yV 'aBThYNV 'yL-DBUrY HSPhUr HZH L'yShVTh KKL-HKThVB 'yLYNV.
VYLK ChLQYHV HKHN V'aChYQM V'yKBVUr VShPhN V'yShYH 'aL-ChLDH HNBY'aH 'aShTh ShLM BN-ThQVH BN-ChUrChS ShMUr HBGDYM VHY'a YShBTh BYUrVShLM BMShNH VYDBUrV 'aLYH.
VTh'aMUr 'aLYHM KH-'aMUr YHVH 'aLHY YShUr'aL 'aMUrV L'aYSh 'aShUr-ShLCh 'aThKM 'aLY.
KH 'aMUr YHVH HNNY MBY'a Ur'yH 'aL-HMQVM HZH V'yL-YShBYV 'aTh KL-DBUrY HSPhUr 'aShUr QUr'a MLK YHVDH.
ThChTh 'aShUr 'yZBVNY VYQTUrV L'aLHYM 'aChUrYM LM'yN HK'yYSNY BKL M'yShH YDYHM VNTShThH ChMThY BMQVM HZH VL'a ThKBH.
V'aL-MLK YHVDH HShLCh 'aThKM LDUrSh 'aTh-YHVH KH Th'aMUrV 'aLYV KH-'aMUr YHVH 'aLHY YShUr'aL HDBUrYM 'aShUr ShM'yTh.
Y'yN UrK-LBBK VThKN'y MPhNY YHVH BShM'yK 'aShUr DBUrThY 'yL-HMQVM HZH V'yL- YShBYV LHYVTh LShMH VLQLLH VThQUr'y 'aTh-BGDYK VThBKH LPhNY VGM 'aNKY ShM'yThY N'aM-YHVH.
